narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Southwest Ambulance of Tucson INC is a Ambulance  Land Transport provider based in Tucson, AZ. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $98.5M in Medicaid payments across 503K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $98.5M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
